{"tid":2145903,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"同情盧偉聰？721、831、新屋嶺、中大、理大？","createTime":"2020-08-08T09:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T10:32:46.000Z","uid":4783,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c60f65abd1c484dbf07f3d7ddfe67ea9b71adfb6","tid":2145903,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰一家在美國。<br />\n11人制裁名單，只有一人沒有任何官職在身。退休大半年的盧偉聰，手持每月豐厚退休金，投奔美國懷抱，與留學美國的24歲兒子團聚。<br />\n人類總是善忘，有人開始同情這位前一哥。其實反修例運動，頭半年時間是由他主導鎮壓。<br />\n721、831、新屋嶺、中大，甚至理大，他參與其中，有份將黑寫成白。<br />\n拍拍籮袖，遠離是非，飛到自由國度，食兩家茶禮，世上有這麼便宜的事？<br />\n他不受3萬散仔歡迎，是首位沒人替他歡送的一哥。<br />\n他不受13億人歡迎，全家被視為漢奸看待。<br />\n他也不受香港人歡迎，因為他要為自己做過的事，奶過的共負責。<br />\n最慘的，是沒有人替他寫「拿石頭砸自己的腳」、「不會得逞」聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kaminghk/posts/310488193633718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkaminghk%2Fposts%2F310488193633718&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=0bfb28cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kaminghk/posts/310488193633718</a>"},{"pid":"84d781df4ba412ca7f9d4e9a4ccbed5281ee9a50","tid":2145903,"uid":24345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"有人開始同情這位前一哥<br />\n<br />\nStockholm Syndrome dumb fuck"},{"pid":"ca2de1f085c8f39c6cdabaa318968c7035f7685b","tid":2145903,"uid":23707,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"明眼人都知係時任二佬話事嘅啦<br />\n不過無一個無磨菇，3萬thx"},{"pid":"1573e85c39d20b3095dc6adce69002aa73fca597","tid":2145903,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"直接拉佢去坐監，凍結資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c720720b8f882bac2a875ff1b8f372ab5990437e","tid":2145903,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca2de1f085c8f39c6cdabaa318968c7035f7685b","tid":2145903,"uid":23707,"l